                                        <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 2px; text-align:center; width: 30%;">የዕቃው ስም<br />Description</td>
                                        <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 2px; text-align:center;">መለኪያ<br />UOM</td>
                                        <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 2px; text-align:center;">ብዛት<br />Qty.</td>
